                                    </img>
                                </p>
                            </p>
                        </p>
                    </td>
                    <td class="TableStyle-callout-table-BodyA-Column2-Body1">
                        <p>Off</p>
                    </td>
                </tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>
        <div class="note" MadCap:conditions="RegionSpecificConditions.CA">
            <p MadCap:conditions="RegionSpecificConditions.CA">The vehicle sets the lights to Auto mode under the following conditions:</p>
            <ul MadCap:conditions="RegionSpecificConditions.CA">
                <li>
                    <p>The lighting mode is set to Parking lights or Off, and you drive faster than the speed of <MadCap:snippetText src="../../../../Resources/Snippets/imperial-metric.flsnp" MadCap:snippetVariables="measure.imperial-unit:mph,;measure.metric-unit:km/h,;measure.metric-value:10,;measure.imperial-value:6,"></MadCap:snippetText>.</p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <p>The vehicle wakes from sleep.</p>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <p>If the lights are set to  Lights + rear fog, Lights, or Auto, the headlights also feature the following: </p>
        <ul>
            <li>
                <p>
                    <b>Dynamic Steering Headlights:</b>&#160;Both the low beams and high beams follow the steering angle to brighten the path while you turn the vehicle. </p>
                <p>
                    <img src="../../../../Resources/Images/print/adaptive-lighting-gen2-steering-r1s-print.svg" MadCap:conditions="OutputTypeConditions.Print-all" alt="dynamic steering headlights" />
                </p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>
                    <b>Dynamic Low Beams Leveling:</b>&#160;The low beams adjust their beam path so they project light evenly if the vehicle pitches backwards as it accelerates or pitches forward as it slows. </p>
                <p>
                    <img src="../../../../Resources/Images/print/adaptive-lighting-gen2-low-beams-leveling-r1s-print.svg" MadCap:conditions="OutputTypeConditions.Print-all" alt="dynamic low beams leveling" />
                </p>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </body>
